text: Jitia Tiberius Caesar pondro saal raj kori thaka homoi te, aru Pontius Pilate pora Judea laga governor thaka homoi te, aru Herod bhi Galilee laga ekjon sthaniya cholawta thakise, aru tai laga kokai Philip bhi eturaea aru Trachonitis laga cholawta thakise, aru Lysanias bhi Abilene laga ekjon cholawta thakise,
